###

### Register a New Account (Admin User)
POST http://localhost:5000/account/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Admin",
  "department": "Library",
  "roll_no": "LB001",
  "mobile": "9874561230",
  "password": "0000",
  "is_admin": true,
  "profile_image": "admin.jpg"
}

###

### Get All Accounts
GET http://localhost:5000/account/
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get Single Account by Roll No
GET http://localhost:5000/account/CS2021001
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Update Account (Partial Update)
PUT http://localhost:5000/account/CS2021001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Updated",
  "mobile": "9123456780",
  "department": "Information Technology"
}

###

### Update Account Password
PUT http://localhost:5000/account/CS2021001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "newSecurePassword@456"
}

###

### Update Profile Image
PUT http://localhost:5000/account/CS2021001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "profile_image": "https://example.com/images/johndoe_new.jpg"
}

###

### Promote Account to Admin
PUT http://localhost:5000/account/CS2021001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "is_admin": true
}

###

### Delete Account
DELETE http://localhost:5000/account/CS2021001
Content-Type: application/json


### ─────────────────────────────────────────
### BOOK ROUTES - REST CLIENT
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Get All Books
GET http://localhost:5000/book/
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get Single Book by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/book/BK001
Content-Type: application/json

###

